<h2 class="bold font-l">Luke is Shocked by Palpatine</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Palpatine loves using Force lightning to torture people. Just ask Maul, Mace, and Luke. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ElectricTorture" class='trope-example-link'>Electric Torture</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="icpqre" data-video-descrip="A powerful Sith Lord who prefers using the Force over a lightsaber as a weapon, and has access to the most arcane arts of the Dark Side " data-video-title="Palpatine" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/icpqre_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/icpqre.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/EvilSorcerer" data-video-tropename="Evil Sorcerer" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/StarWarsRebelsS4E11AWorldBetweenWorlds,WesternAnimation/StarWarsRebels,Characters/StarWarsEmperorPalpatine" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/icpqre.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Palpatine</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
